        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[🦷#世界口腔健康日# 牙疼不是病，疼起来真要命！每天都刷牙，怎么还有烂牙[抓狂] 牙龈出血、口腔异味、蛀牙……很多问题都是由于牙齿的清理没做到位！那#没有...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[🦷<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%8F%A3%E8%85%94%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E6%97%A5%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#世界口腔健康日#</span></a> 牙疼不是病，疼起来真要命！每天都刷牙，怎么还有烂牙<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[抓狂]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_zhuakuang-c007ffb7fe.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> 牙龈出血、口腔异味、蛀牙……很多问题都是由于牙齿的清理没做到位！<br><br>那<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E7%89%99%E9%BD%BF%E4%B9%9F%E8%A6%81%E5%88%B7%E7%89%99%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E7%89%99%E9%BD%BF%E4%B9%9F%E8%A6%81%E5%88%B7%E7%89%99%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#没有牙齿也要刷牙吗#</span></a>？刷牙其实是清洁整个口腔环境，包括牙齿、牙龈面和舌部。虽然没有牙齿，但黏膜、牙龈、牙槽等组织是在的！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>卫提醒大家：即使没有牙齿，也要坚持刷牙哦~最后，跟着卫再复习一遍爱牙护齿的正确姿势<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[开学季]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/72/2021_kaixueji_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（健康中国）<img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnx9qhzyz2j20go0m841b.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnx9qi0t11j20go0m8tah.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnx9qhz8m9j20go0m8q4d.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnx9qi2yghj20go0m8dhp.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnx9qhz6maj20go0m8760.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnx9qi0e30j20go0m8dhm.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnx9qi04b1j20go0m876g.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnx9qi1o0sj20go0m8gnz.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnx9qhzeqyj20go0m8mz7.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
