            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[疑问]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yiwen-40c066d5c3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%BB%B4%E7%94%9F%E7%B4%A0B2%E8%83%BD%E6%B2%BB%E7%96%97%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E5%8F%A3%E8%85%94%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%BB%B4%E7%94%9F%E7%B4%A0B2%E8%83%BD%E6%B2%BB%E7%96%97%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E5%8F%A3%E8%85%94%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#维生素B2能治疗这些口腔疾病#</span></a> ？】补充维生素B2能治疗口腔溃疡？北京大学口腔医院的专家来辟谣啦！维生素B2对治疗口角炎、唇炎等口腔黏膜病有帮助，但它并不能直接治疗口腔溃疡哦<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[NO]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/h_buyao-3a904f27f5.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>，而<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E5%8F%A3%E8%85%94%E6%BA%83%E7%96%A1%E8%A1%A5VB%E5%92%8CVC%E6%9B%B4%E9%9D%A0%E8%B0%B1%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E5%8F%A3%E8%85%94%E6%BA%83%E7%96%A1%E8%A1%A5VB%E5%92%8CVC%E6%9B%B4%E9%9D%A0%E8%B0%B1%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#预防口腔溃疡补VB和VC更靠谱#</span></a> 👇🏻（CCTV生活圈）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:5012884783300611" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1ly1hntuzh0pk4j20u01hc76y.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/zhZozRt7lx08dlSPlk5y010412008eWk0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1280.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1710921901&amp;ssig=4s%2FEiwEmC%2B&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/0BbMJZdClx08dlSP2thK010412004zpz0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1710921901&amp;ssig=6vw93XzS21&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/QEULM1vUlx08dlSO4ZAQ010412002ptn0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x640.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1710921901&amp;ssig=DOyJrismyL&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A5012884783300611" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
